[h1]Phobos' Industrial Pathways: Pathology[/h1]

[b]Version:[/b] 0.1.0
[b]Requires:[/b] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3668598865]PhobosLib[/url]
[b]PZ Version:[/b] Build 42.15.0+

[hr][/hr]

Biological specimen acquisition and processing for Project Zomboid Build 42. Core pillars: cadaver processing, specimen extractions, biohazard handling, laboratory analysis, and pathogen research. Focuses on virology and pathology rather than general chemistry.

[h2]Features (v0.1.0)[/h2]

[h3]Proximity Autopsy Table[/h3]
Right-click near corpses within range of a [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3399491432]Zombie Virus Vaccine[/url] Autopsy Table to perform table-quality autopsies without manually placing corpses. The context menu lists all nearby corpses with full ZVV tooltip info (freshness, zombie status, organs, equipment).

[h3]RV Bridge Remote Autopsy[/h3]
If no local autopsy table is found but a [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3371837498]PROJECT RV Interior[/url] vehicle with a morgue table is parked nearby, offers "Autopsy (RV Lab Table)" to relay the autopsy through the RV's table. Just visit your RV interior once to register the table — it stays cached even after exiting.

[h2]Sandbox Options[/h2]

[list]
[*] [b]Enable Proximity Autopsy[/b] (default: on) — Toggle the proximity table context menu
[*] [b]Autopsy Table Range[/b] (default: 3, range: 1–6) — Tile radius for detecting nearby tables
[*] [b]Enable RV Bridge[/b] (default: on) — Toggle the RV Bridge remote autopsy feature
[*] [b]RV Vehicle Search Range[/b] (default: 5, range: 1–10) — Tile radius for detecting nearby RVs
[*] [b]Enable Debug Logging[/b] (default: off) — Verbose console output for troubleshooting
[/list]

[h2]Dependencies[/h2]

[b]Required:[/b]
[list]
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3668598865]PhobosLib[/url] — Shared utility library
[/list]

[b]Optional (soft dependencies):[/b]
[list]
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3399491432]Zombie Virus Vaccine[/url] (ZVV) — Provides the autopsy system and morgue table
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3371837498]PROJECT RV Interior[/url] — RV interior rooms for the RV Bridge feature
[/list]

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]

PIP is designed for cross-mod harmony. All soft dependencies are runtime-detected — installing PIP without ZVV or the RV mod will not cause errors; those features simply won't appear.

